{"word":"Bigotry","slug":"bigotry","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bigotry</b> General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=5'>Isa 65:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2&verse=16'>Mar 2:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=2'>Luk 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=50'>Luk 9:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=14'>Luk 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=28'>Act 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=45'>Act 10:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=13'>Act 18:13</a><br/> Paul's argument against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=23'>Rom 3:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=16'>Rom 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=25'>Rom 4:25</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Of Joshua, through envy seeking to suppress Eldad and Medad who were prophesying<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=29'>Num 11:29</a> <br/> - Of Jews:<br/> b With regard to the Samaritans<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=9'>Joh 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=27'>Joh 4:27</a><br/> b in rejecting the teachings of Jesus at Nazareth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=28'>Luk 4:28</a><br/> b in falsely accusing Jesus:<br/> b of blasphemy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=18'>Joh 5:18</a><br/> b of being a gluttonous man and winebibber<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=19'>Mat 11:19</a><br/> b of keeping company with sinners<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=39'>Luk 7:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=2'>Luk 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=19&verse=7'>Luk 19:7</a><br/> b of not conforming to the traditions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=39'>Luk 11:39</a><br/> b in their treatment of the young man who was born blind, whom Jesus restored to sight<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=29'>Joh 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=34'>Joh 9:34</a><br/> b With regard to Paul's preaching<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=29'>Act 21:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=22'>Act 22:22</a><br/> - Of the Samaritans in refusing to receive Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=53'>Luk 9:53</a> <br/> - Of the disciples in forbidding children to be brought to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=13'>Mat 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=13'>Mar 10:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=15'>Luk 18:15</a> <br/> - Of the early Christians:<br/> b in opposing the preaching of the gospel to the Gentiles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=45'>Act 10:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=3'>Act 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=25'>Act 21:25</a><br/> b in regard to circumcision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=10'>Act 15:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=24'>Act 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=5'>Gal 2:5</a><br/> - In zeal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=10&verse=3'>Rom 10:3</a> <br/> - In persecutions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=2&verse=16'>1Th 2:16</a> <br/> - Of John in forbidding the casting out of devils by one who did not follow Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=40'>Mar 9:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=50'>Luk 9:50</a> <br/> - Of James and John in desiring to call down fire upon the Samaritans who would not receive Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=56'>Luk 9:56</a> <br/> - Of Saul, in persecuting the Christians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=4'>Act 22:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=5'>Act 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=9'>Act 26:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=14'>Gal 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=6'>Phi 3:6</a><br/><a href='S:Intolerance, Religious'>Intolerance, Religious</a>; <a href='S:Persecution'>Persecution</a>; <a href='S:Uncharitableness'>Uncharitableness</a> "}]}